sequenceDiagram
    participant M as RocketMQ
    participant C1 as 消费者1
    participant C2 as 消费者2
    participant P as PostgreSQL

    M->>C1: message_id=M1
    M->>C2: message_id=M1

    C1->>P: INSERT inbox(M1)
    C2->>P: INSERT inbox(M1)

    Note over P: 唯一键使两个事务串行判定

    P-->>C1: 插入成功
    C1->>P: 创建订单并提交
    P-->>C2: ON CONFLICT，未插入

    C1-->>M: ACK
    C2-->>M: ACK，返回既有结果
